{"tid":2454331,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Snapchat啲推介內容咁獵奇？","createTime":"2021-03-20T07:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T07:31:49.000Z","uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd7094f49752367e45447c0e17c7911ce648352","tid":2454331,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"樓主我用sc同朋友儲火，唔會㩒落去佢啲推介內容<br />\n<br />\n最近先留意到佢推介啲野都好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多張連體嬰嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人做gym個胸肌好似籃球咁漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲就係睇落有個好大，睇落去好痛嘅傷口，但原來係畫出嚟/貼咗貼紙上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地就咁睇文字描述可能覺得冇乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無心理準備嘅情況下，突然間睇到都會有少少嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106e5cf83e20153c253ee5e393c2cd09a4f85edc","tid":2454331,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"未必去到獵奇，但好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835a4547052d141baefbc27e22b2b6b6c9c346a2","tid":2454331,"uid":24345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"Snapchat同抖音鬥影響心智"},{"pid":"c2081755951886da9c79cda82b80af7e78e7ab65","tid":2454331,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"講明先，樓主我唔係細膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要我對住啲屍體相食飯都冇問題<br />\n但你要提前話我知俾我做下心理準備<br />\n而依家sc就好似將呢啲內容一野撻落你塊面度咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005b138c936f8016cea43ef0ae44bb9b193f97ff","tid":2454331,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"835a4547052d141baefbc27e22b2b6b6c9c346a2","tid":2454331,"uid":24345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"Snapchat同抖音鬥影響心智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢推介啲內容好奇怪"},{"pid":"1d80b57f8ab587be0ac204f2021af4d5ec363d80","tid":2454331,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"005b138c936f8016cea43ef0ae44bb9b193f97ff","tid":2454331,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"835a4547052d141baefbc27e22b2b6b6c9c346a2","tid":2454331,"uid":24345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"Snapchat同抖音鬥影響心智"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢推介啲內容好奇怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"自從俾ig抄咗story 之後Snapchat 只能夠行依種垃圾content farm feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84506c95868bf1c98811379bc46a31797df6deb0","tid":2454331,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"個名隔離有個星座符好戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}